{"thig8.1:0.1":"Therigatha 8.1 ","thig8.1:0.2":"Atthakanipata ","thig8.1:0.3":"Sisupacalatherigatha ","thig8.1:1.1":"“Bhikkhuni silasampanna, ","thig8.1:1.2":"indriyesu susamvuta; ","thig8.1:1.3":"Adhigacche padam santam, ","thig8.1:1.4":"asecanakamojavam”. ","thig8.1:2.1":"“Tavatimsa ca yama ca, ","thig8.1:2.2":"tusita capi devata; ","thig8.1:2.3":"Nimmanaratino deva, ","thig8.1:2.4":"ye deva vasavattino; ","thig8.1:2.5":"Tattha cittam panidhehi, ","thig8.1:2.6":"yattha te vusitam pure”. ","thig8.1:3.1":"“Tavatimsa ca yama ca, ","thig8.1:3.2":"tusita capi devata; ","thig8.1:3.3":"Nimmanaratino deva, ","thig8.1:3.4":"ye deva vasavattino. ","thig8.1:4.1":"Kalam kalam bhavabhavam, ","thig8.1:4.2":"sakkayasmim purakkhata; ","thig8.1:4.3":"Avitivatta sakkayam, ","thig8.1:4.4":"jatimaranasarino. ","thig8.1:5.1":"Sabbo adipito loko, ","thig8.1:5.2":"sabbo loko padipito; ","thig8.1:5.3":"Sabbo pajjalito loko, ","thig8.1:5.4":"sabbo loko pakampito. ","thig8.1:6.1":"Akampiyam atuliyam, ","thig8.1:6.2":"aputhujjanasevitam; ","thig8.1:6.3":"Buddho dhammamadesesi, ","thig8.1:6.4":"tattha me nirato mano. ","thig8.1:7.1":"Tassaham vacanam sutva, ","thig8.1:7.2":"viharim sasane rata; ","thig8.1:7.3":"Tisso vijja anuppatta, ","thig8.1:7.4":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","thig8.1:8.1":"Sabbattha vihata nandi, ","thig8.1:8.2":"tamokhandho padalito; ","thig8.1:8.3":"Evam janahi papima, ","thig8.1:8.4":"nihato tvamasi antaka”. ","thig8.1:9.1":"… Sisupacala theri …. ","thig8.1:10.1":"Atthakanipato nitthito. "}